{"tid":2128831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（武漢肺炎）你哋點樣反駁啲深藍？","createTime":"2020-07-28T08:01:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-28T08:20:31.000Z","uid":353266,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4052b77ed32c9765c306fe8dc5b61ed29f8ecbcd","tid":2128831,"uid":353266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"我好奇而家啲藍絲究竟點睇柒婆，所以入咗去星島日報呢啲藍到發紫嘅圍爐區睇評論。點知，我發現入面啲深藍仲係好支持柒婆不突止，佢哋仲話武肺大爆發係唔關豁免檢疫政策事。我見入面有好多深藍都會咁反駁啲專家：<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">「豁免檢疫政策早已經喺二月實施。如果真係咁，咁點解香港過咗咁多個月，先會有大爆發出現呢？」</span><br />\n<br />\n你哋會點反駁佢哋呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e440851e814e3935e18b3ffdef8d1bec7f2d79","tid":2128831,"uid":264871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"9/6先放寬架"},{"pid":"a54560af550906ba7dabbee0f7e9fab7d7435b4c","tid":2128831,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:02:54.000Z","msg":"因為外國而家嘅疫情爆得比2月嚴重"},{"pid":"6ac0c1e34e1a474fabd789c2d92841c5aa513687","tid":2128831,"uid":240374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:03:46.000Z","msg":"因為當時香港人未有鬆懈"},{"pid":"ef69bc33e292ff5dba97ed3d741772262caa8fdb","tid":2128831,"uid":264871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70e440851e814e3935e18b3ffdef8d1bec7f2d79","tid":2128831,"uid":264871,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:02:51.000Z","msg":"9/6先放寬架"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:04:05.000Z","msg":"6月9號比人直接換班"},{"pid":"e550a40cf453fdeae2b1024a9c71de73c8a64c7e","tid":2128831,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"改變唔到佢立場既，無謂哂時間，唔洗駁"},{"pid":"e98db1b7862e7c33539179b031ed6ca7f6874370","tid":2128831,"uid":190005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"因為佢哋呢一兩個月就開始鬆懈"},{"pid":"2e68742bd3c2672c7dee61d2ba6d79657504c987","tid":2128831,"uid":51529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:06:16.000Z","msg":"有漏洞唔代表會即時爆發<br />\n事實今次爆發好大機會係因為免檢疫<br />\n唔好偷換概念<br />\n你屌閪屌穿左個安全套都唔代表一定會成孕<br />\n但會大大增加成孕風險"},{"pid":"aec32ba32f625c55f4c65aea3e36f01aa4c15335","tid":2128831,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:08:47.000Z","msg":"唔戴套屌閪都唔係包生仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0e3c5af2ac305aabf8ba010a3d117693ddaddb","tid":2128831,"uid":353266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e550a40cf453fdeae2b1024a9c71de73c8a64c7e","tid":2128831,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:04:46.000Z","msg":"改變唔到佢立場既，無謂哂時間，唔洗駁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:09:49.000Z","msg":"呢啲唔係講緊改變佢哋立場，而係話佢哋有位反駁嘅話，就會攞呢個論點去洗版，洗部份中間派同啲淺藍嘅腦。<br />\n<br />\n七二一單嘢已經有個版俾你睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ec3b86cdd0b9f5d991e348492a55ad31602ae29","tid":2128831,"uid":327462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"過咗成年仲諗點駁藍屍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}